<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٦٧٦٢ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/6700">أَبُو الْوَلِيدِ، </a>حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةَ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسٍ، </a>عَنِ النَّبِيِّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span> قَالَ: <span class="c2">«ابْنُ أُخْتِ الْقَوْمِ مِنْهُمْ أَوْ مِنْ أَنْفُسِهِمْ.»</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>